{"type": "article", "id": 38035, "title": "想为房间调个香？试试这个智能香氛机｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-02-21T23:16:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 37888, "name": "& Smith"}, {"id": 37889, "name": "Pejac"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 383, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170221225220XT3v62xtPcLrUOWz.gif", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Moodo</h3><p>尽管智能家居的功能越来越丰富，要打造独特的室内香氛往往还是需要用传统的香薰蜡烛或是机器，香型也比较单一。最近，来自美国的初创公司 Moodo 就填补了这一领域的空缺，带来了同名的智能香氛机。机器上配有四个胶囊槽，使用时只需要装入配套的胶囊，就可以通过手机 app 控制它们各自的浓度，调配出各式各样的香味。如果你摸索到了自己喜欢的味道，不仅可以将当前设置收藏起来，还能将它分享给朋友。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/moodo-the-smart-home-fragrance-box--2#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 149 美元，内含一套主题胶囊（4 种香型）。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225301sEj53TMIz1CmFlv4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556250\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225259tNyTHSIq03pCb5Ra.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225301xymYE0reLW3sNk8q.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225259iZQj2YxP6LV9CEdm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644262\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Memo Box Mini by Tinylogics</h3><p>按时服药听起来很容易，但并不是人人都能做到。成立于 2014 年的英国研发团队 <a href=\"http://www.tinylogics.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tinylogics</a> 为此做过一项调查，结果发现有半数患者因为种种原因没有遵循指示服药，因此影响治疗效果。Tinylogics 为此设计了一款名为 Memo Box Mini 的智能药盒，通过蓝牙与手机相连后，它会根据专用 app 内设置好的时间表提醒患者服药，家属也可以通过 app 检查服药情况，甚至向患者的手机发送震动或者拨打电话进行人工提醒。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/661527809/smart-pillbox/\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 20 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225628W6ltLIpzUy4v8MHh.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563272\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225628wVXQ2OsrpWaP1m4u.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225640VAeUX2SJwk6gyrF0.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225639EfbDe9TLk2c3n4Rh.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225629irMNWl1twZmHOAfK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Origami Bulletproof Shield</h3><p>如果你留心过影视剧中执法人员的枪战场景，或许会发现那些由中世纪盾牌演变而来的防弹屏障不仅沉重，而且通常也只能掩护一个人。为了在提供有效保护的同时，让执法人员能够“轻装上阵”，来自美国杨百翰大学（Brigham Young University）的研究团队借鉴一种名为 Yoshimura 的折纸图案，推出了这款可以灵活调节的<a href=\"https://news.byu.edu/news/byu-researchers-built-bullet-proof-origami-shield-protect-law-enforcement\" rel=\"nofollow\">防弹屏障</a>。这些折纸屏障在重量上只是现有屏障的一半，只需要五秒就能完全打开，为两到三人提供掩护。不使用的时候它们能够紧凑地折叠起来，提升了搬运的效率。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225352fQwpsUILJKuaR8Ng.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225351XtQCGgqdvpiS54WD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.207824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225351Ty9tPL3wENsW84xq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702212253516fHG0qMUadchyzE7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225351km1lhHxW89EZ3pCe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Downside up by Pejac</h3><p>在国外一些城市的街头，当你抬头望向街灯或是电线，有时会发现被扔在上面的鞋子，这种独特的街头文化被称为 Shoefiti，意指用鞋涂鸦。如果你最近刚好在东伦敦地区，你或许会发现一幕奇观，鞋子呈倒立状悬挂在街灯上，像是定格在了将它们抛上去的某个瞬间。这些充满幽默感的反重力景观其实是由西班牙艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.pejac.es/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pejac</a> 创作的，他希望可以借此鼓励人们用不同的视角看待周围的景观，从看似寻常的事物中发现艺术的存在。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225424NeyDKIwAf5kHgQoM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225421SWnXLJwTtKfNds7c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.756724\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225422ONPaME12Zzc7gXTp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225423vOVd8ks95omlx2DM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.212714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Design Seeds by Jessica Colaluca</h3><p>如果你正为了衣着或是设计上的色彩搭配犯愁，不妨在设计师 Jessica Colaluca 创立的色彩图鉴网站 <a href=\"https://www.design-seeds.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Seeds</a> 寻找灵感。对色彩抱有极大热情的 Colaluca 擅长从周遭事物中找到某种特定的搭配，她会将照片中的颜色提取出来，制作成一张张简洁明了的搭配示意图，并配上颜色的代码供人们使用。由于搭配越来越多，Colaluca 还为网站开辟了不同类别的索引，你可以按照主题系列或是以某一特定颜色进行浏览。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225448XojUgrK7PvJBTml6.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.909699\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225449B2S6XhJFQGlcCL57.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.909699\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225449AMFfK5Datj8WO4lx.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.105396\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225450HR8hmyiDYAK6dQ2F.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.904087\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225451bAtkgEnwBlK2RcuG.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.908710\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225451qlB6ybGY40JZQIHi.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.103275\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Elderbrook by &amp; Smith</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.elderbrookdrinks.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Elderbrook</a> 是一个来自英国的果味饮料品牌，这组充满活力的包装是由当地创意机构 <a href=\"http://andsmithdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">&amp; Smith</a> 操刀设计的。为了营造出特立独行的感觉，&amp; Smith 邀请了三位插画家为旗下的九种混合型口味绘制了风格各异的印象图，并要求他们将所使用的水果原料巧妙地融合进作品中。除此之外，每种饮料的标签上还印有三行充满讽刺意味的标语，比如“这不是家庭装”、“这不是官方合作品牌”、“这没有抗衰老”功效等等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225506uLWmtUKfrGgHaw1c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225506NLARxMcyu2jdr9QG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170221225506lkNXy3ftQiYpVaI8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.494000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702212255062BRv7HhtNXf9jUx8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.494000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}